
1. https://miktex.org/download
2. https://ghostscript.com/releases/gsdnld.html
3. latex --version
4. dvisvgm --version
5. Create a file with
```
\documentclass[tikz]{standalone}
\begin{document}
\begin{tikzpicture}
    \draw[thick, red] (0,0) -- (2,2);
    \node[draw] at (1,1) {Success!};
\end{tikzpicture}
\end{document}
```
6. cd tikz_v2
7. latex --output-directory=temp input/test_1.tex 
8. dvisvgm --no-fonts --output=output/test_1.svg temp/test_1.dvi